    <briefdescription>
<para>The <ref refid="struct_x_usb___config" kindref="compound">XUsb_Config</ref> structure contains configuration information for the USB controller. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This structure only contains the basic configuration for the device. The caller also needs to initialize the USB device controller with the <ref refid="group__usb_1ga9c50c0ee6d36d4b87a40018c2ad0fd25" kindref="member">XUsb_ConfigureDevice()</ref> function call. </para>    </detaileddescription>
